      "rationale": "NIH is the FDA-recognized benchmark metric for pump hemolysis. RH < 1 acceptance criterion directly compares device performance to predicate. Clinical relevance of both QoIs established in regulatory guidance and peer-reviewed literature. Relevance of QoI level 2 satisfied."
